  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "He saw the father cannot continue so he said, I'm staying with my father and they'll probably kill both of us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "We could hear only the shots.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And this was a march.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "We were going and no food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "This is already springtime in Austria, and you see on the fields yellow-- some kind of a grass-- they gave in Europe-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in Hungarian it's called [HUNGARIAN].",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "It is some kind of a flowery-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it's a grass, but it has beautiful, yellowish flower and it tastes good.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And we saw those fields and small as I was, I was bending down and when it comes to it I running and try to fill up my little bag.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Incidentally, we didn't carry anymore packages.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we didn't have the strength.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "However, just before sundown we picked up because the roads were full of packages-- [NON-ENGLISH], dirty shirts and pants and blankets.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I said to myself-- and it wasn't mine-- everybody made this system for themselves.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Just before sundown, we picked up a blanket.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because marching in the daytime, we did not have but we only carried that filling which was the closest, which is still the closest to us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were walking and just before sundown we picked up a blanket there to sleep.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And once it happened, I remember, we made a stop.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And whenever there's a stop, I always ran ahead to the beginning of the group just in case I'm slowing down, I should still be within the group.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because those, they were watching for those who are slow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Those who were slow, they were just plain-- they were sentenced to death.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
